                <head>The Amende</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Spectator had previously included George A. Coffman on a printed "Black
                    List" of subscribers who left the area without paying their bill. Formerly of
                    Sanders' Store in Rockbridge, Coffman moved to Illinois. He has since paid his
                    debt.</summary>
            </div>
